title: Emergency Podcast: Rockets Trade Russell Westbrook to the Wizards for John Wall | The Ringer NBA Show
description:
Logan Murdock, Chris Ryan, and Kevin O’Connor heed the call as the Rockets trade Russell Westbrook to the Wizards for John Wall and a 2023 protected draft pick. 
Don't forget to go find the new feed for 'The Mismatch' on Spotify, Apple, or wherever you get your podcasts.
Hosts: Logan Murdock, Chris Ryan, and Kevin O’Connor
